Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.27,0:00:07.50,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接击中防护罩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.62,0:00:10.42,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 总统还没到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.57,0:00:12.53,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样不是办法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.55,0:00:14.58,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命令Battle Frontier出航
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.51,0:00:17.04,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辅佐官别来发号施令
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.48,0:00:21.73,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,11分钟前 总统的死亡消息已被确认
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.43,0:00:23.72,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Vajra所为
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.97,0:00:29.38,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此这艘代理政府机能的Battle Frontier中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.47,0:00:30.98,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最高级的文官
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.17,0:00:35.92,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是由我接管总统的全部权限
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.08,0:00:38.29,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请立刻执行命令
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.35,0:00:39.37,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.25,0:00:42.09,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这艘Battle Frontier被攻陷的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.25,0:00:43.62,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都完了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.87,0:00:46.43,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这都不明白吗 阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.98,0:00:50.74,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 长官
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.00,0:00:54.77,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Battle Frontier紧急分离
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.17,0:00:57.02,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,启航程序开始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.52,0:01:01.41,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快 他如果夺权…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.91,0:01:07.60,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Battle Frontier出航
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.71,0:01:10.61,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重复 Battle Frontier出航
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.68,0:01:27.32,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 轮到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.90,0:03:06.82,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs50\fad(600,450)\pos(296,695)\shad0\bord2\be1}苍之以太
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.97,0:03:09.48,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去三号岛的话会有办法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.98,0:03:10.57,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.85,0:03:14.50,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葛兰 准备好没
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.54,0:03:18.33,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米歇尔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.60,0:03:44.91,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.55,0:03:52.47,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米歇尔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.08,0:03:55.69,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.91,0:03:56.59,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.92,0:04:04.51,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,17区域敌机接近 数量7
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.71,0:04:06.41,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2，1航母级
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.55,0:04:09.79,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主炮发射状态 来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.80,0:04:10.94,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.20,0:04:17.31,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后方热源出现 这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.14,0:04:28.50,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Battle Frontier
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.96,0:04:33.71,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然这艘船的主炮还有作用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.92,0:04:34.86,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.52,0:04:38.66,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样也许能对付外部的敌人了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.73,0:04:42.36,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 这治标不治本
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.80,0:04:44.36,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,临时总统
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.76,0:04:47.78,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能否安静一下 准将
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.89,0:04:52.73,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次作战是卢卡？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.86,0:04:54.97,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 19线路
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.94,0:05:03.00,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 本舰直接前往击退外部来袭的Vajra
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.50,0:05:05.25,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与Quarter接通线路
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.29,0:05:07.91,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3号岛屿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.08,0:05:16.05,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.28,0:05:17.34,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Little Girl
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.89,0:05:20.65,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分割并吞噬半径50公里的空间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.89,0:05:23.46,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LAI开发的空间炸弹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.89,0:05:27.26,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,50公里 不会连船团都吃掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.63,0:05:30.53,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 把Vajra集中在某处
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.77,0:05:31.79,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让它爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.98,0:05:32.72,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.64,0:05:39.17,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢卡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.18,0:05:40.02,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鲁多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.11,0:05:42.68,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道卢卡 你小子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.45,0:05:48.45,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我决定了 一定要保护
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.65,0:05:50.57,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.02,0:05:56.87,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就要兰歌去做诱饵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.58,0:05:59.51,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米歇尔前辈都死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.72,0:06:03.11,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船也伤痕累累
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.34,0:06:05.08,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生态系统混乱不堪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.79,0:06:09.05,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再受害的话Frontier就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.58,0:06:12.33,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这已经是赌上生存权的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.02,0:06:15.04,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们和Vajra谁能生存
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.40,0:06:18.61,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸存的是它们还是我们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.25,0:06:22.54,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许我们正站在这节骨眼上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.23,0:06:33.31,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会唱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.36,0:06:38.29,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了大家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.08,0:06:44.29,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真打算这么做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.99,0:06:48.91,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3号岛是受创最轻的岛屿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.32,0:06:53.53,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本是天顶星人用的农业观光岛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.51,0:06:57.07,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小人化后收容也更便利
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.41,0:06:59.62,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他岛屿时间不足
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.92,0:07:02.80,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰歌开始唱歌后
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.08,0:07:05.78,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vajra应该会从所有舰船那里聚集过来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.53,0:07:08.17,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认移动开始后
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.34,0:07:09.91,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分离三号岛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.41,0:07:12.29,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远离安全圈后
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.45,0:07:13.90,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引爆它
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.74,0:07:20.46,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在这里一直歌唱到最后瞬间是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.66,0:07:25.11,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这之前绝对不让Vajra接近
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.76,0:07:27.73,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也一定会让你安全脱出
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.50,0:07:29.26,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.29,0:07:35.90,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心唱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.89,0:07:39.56,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.62,0:07:42.44,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次应该能行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.09,0:07:45.85,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.68,0:08:03.72,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想唱的话别勉强 兰歌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.87,0:08:10.71,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太过分了 布瑞拉先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.32,0:08:13.81,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.70,0:08:19.56,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌是你的心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.65,0:08:23.51,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是只属于你的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.17,0:08:38.81,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 布瑞拉先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.19,0:08:40.14,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过没事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.36,0:08:52.21,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想传达给唯一的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.74,0:08:59.26,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这首歌虽然没能被他接受
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.79,0:09:05.34,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是唯一的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.47,0:09:23.29,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 我在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.49,0:09:44.31,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.68,0:09:52.20,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主岛上的Vajra陆续向三号岛移动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.79,0:10:00.84,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢对七濑…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.91,0:10:06.18,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就现在 加大攻势
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.25,0:10:08.75,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么袭击我们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.83,0:10:15.06,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米歇尔 米歇尔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.53,0:10:30.21,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛 好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.90,0:10:34.88,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得漂亮 小公主
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.81,0:10:38.92,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和11年前大不相同了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.18,0:10:44.14,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分离三号岛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.45,0:10:57.04,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认兰歌·李脱出
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.66,0:10:58.65,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.20,0:11:25.30,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.56,0:11:28.04,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干得好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.64,0:11:31.98,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 兰歌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.56,0:11:38.13,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.08,0:11:41.95,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牺牲得太多
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.62,0:11:58.91,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是一场令人心痛的灾难
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.76,0:12:03.24,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们失去了敬爱的霍华德·葛拉斯总统
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.95,0:12:10.12,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有众多人失去朋友亲人和至爱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.11,0:12:15.67,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家怀着愤怒与悲伤一定想问
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.74,0:12:17.93,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.72,0:12:20.26,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么是我们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.65,0:12:23.19,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我的家人 恋人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.64,0:12:26.10,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们为什么会受伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.17,0:12:30.24,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总动员残存兵力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.72,0:12:33.28,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,残存的Vajra也几乎全部扫荡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.03,0:12:36.29,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事态终于趋于稳定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.29,0:12:41.06,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但失去的人与物再也无法挽回
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.86,0:12:46.01,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家心中一定也留下难以抹去的伤痕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.01,0:12:57.03,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 伤痕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.75,0:12:59.71,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受伤太深
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.81,0:13:02.51,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在让我们衷心祈祷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.10,0:13:05.06,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为逝去的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.68,0:13:12.79,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰歌小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.32,0:13:19.62,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的哥哥 奥兹马·李少校也下落不明
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.91,0:13:22.65,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定很难过
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.63,0:13:25.54,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但还能为我们献上一曲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.34,0:13:29.33,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,象征追悼与明日希望的歌曲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.05,0:13:35.30,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为我们能在与Vajra的战斗中获胜并幸存
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.41,0:13:47.75,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.95,0:13:49.89,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰歌小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.85,0:13:54.13,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.24,0:13:59.86,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再也不能唱了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.45,0:14:08.27,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰歌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.38,0:14:10.41,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰歌？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.27,0:14:26.84,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受够了 为什么是我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.88,0:14:31.82,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我的歌对Vajra们…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.96,0:14:37.89,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小爱？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.68,0:14:46.12,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小爱 你去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.28,0:14:47.65,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长那么大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.70,0:14:50.41,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在担心你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.97,0:15:04.75,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小爱？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.92,0:15:15.52,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深更半夜是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.84,0:15:18.53,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰歌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.25,0:15:34.97,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰歌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.85,0:15:37.76,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鲁多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.29,0:15:41.34,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰歌 你为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.35,0:15:43.72,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个请求 阿鲁多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.98,0:15:46.80,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.89,0:15:52.43,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 阿鲁多一直带着的纸飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.80,0:15:54.57,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能教我怎么折吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.49,0:16:14.76,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问件事可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.48,0:16:18.86,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鲁多为什么想去天空飞行？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.34,0:16:22.37,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.10,0:16:31.32,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我母亲体弱多病 总是看着天空
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.51,0:16:33.96,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一起看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.65,0:16:37.27,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时母亲说了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.82,0:16:40.76,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想看真正的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.49,0:16:42.26,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.66,0:16:50.28,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,湛蓝 无边无际的地平线和白云
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.34,0:16:54.49,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样真正的自由的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.82,0:16:58.56,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像童话一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.20,0:17:01.32,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对出生在这艘船上的我来说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.28,0:17:03.27,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.38,0:17:12.30,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 兰歌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.15,0:17:14.21,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鲁多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.57,0:17:19.58,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.43,0:17:23.22,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.96,0:17:34.18,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.67,0:17:41.57,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让它飞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.72,0:17:43.87,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.25,0:17:45.02,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.03,0:18:10.17,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都…希望自由地活着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.10,0:18:12.09,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.81,0:18:14.76,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鲁多
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.46,0:18:17.37,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.05,0:18:21.30,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.53,0:18:22.18,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vajra
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.55,0:18:23.78,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 阿鲁多
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.61,0:18:25.71,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么阻止我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.39,0:18:27.82,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它可是Vajra
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.95,0:18:29.19,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是它们杀了米歇尔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.32,0:18:30.90,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不是它
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.27,0:18:34.96,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它才刚蜕皮没做过任何坏事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.48,0:18:36.99,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也要杀吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.14,0:18:40.55,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有Vajra在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.89,0:18:42.46,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空就会成为战场
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.65,0:18:48.77,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要活下来只能杀掉他们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.83,0:18:57.66,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.38,0:19:00.31,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布瑞拉先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.72,0:19:03.46,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰歌 说你的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.99,0:19:08.00,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会实现你的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.39,0:19:13.21,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小爱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.02,0:19:15.73,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰歌你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.17,0:19:25.23,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最近渐渐能回忆起过去的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.95,0:19:26.89,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.91,0:19:31.37,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我必须知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.70,0:19:33.07,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.61,0:19:36.97,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.46,0:19:38.43,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.61,0:19:43.93,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少把它带回同伴中去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.99,0:19:47.96,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.17,0:20:10.03,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰歌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.83,0:20:12.79,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鲁多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.43,0:20:16.26,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜 别去兰歌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.26,0:20:24.30,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实想和阿鲁多去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.85,0:20:30.05,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想永远在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.04,0:20:31.79,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰歌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.98,0:20:36.22,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鲁多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.74,0:20:42.70,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见…
